{"tid":1658980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"點解要跟蹤保安？","createTime":"2019-10-16T17:11:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-16T23:20:39.000Z","uid":128304,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"841503ca72f4ce7f4d03a00b93d35bdccc4e5b50","tid":1658980,"uid":128304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T17:11:18.000Z","msg":"我先假設片中嘅的而且確係陳同學<br />\n<br />\n有啲人話行為古怪<br />\n的而且確係好古怪<br />\n但造成古怪嘅成因未必係食咗藥<br />\n我覺得佢係<br />\n跟蹤同觀察嘅行徑嚟<br />\n佢係搵緊個保安巡走路線同觀察緊<br />\n亦都嘗試輕輕力接近<br />\n所以除鞋（自己試過）<br />\n至於點解會落咗街我就唔知唔想亂咁估<br />\n但明顯係搵緊個保安<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yppZYER.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyppZYER.png&h=aeb29762&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/011056_c671c3010dffd84468d8ea3c992bfc5e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F17%2F011056_c671c3010dffd84468d8ea3c992bfc5e.png&h=200de091&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/011058_e947cb0f48e09309c0ff6230d9773da8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F17%2F011058_e947cb0f48e09309c0ff6230d9773da8.png&h=af9014b5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/011059_095e06275ae1547120fa1fb6396c8848.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F17%2F011059_095e06275ae1547120fa1fb6396c8848.png&h=3db82331&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/011100_c323d873e63890f1131cab4d6c120171.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F10%2F17%2F011100_c323d873e63890f1131cab4d6c120171.png&h=5c08fd5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/10/17/011101_ad148735091368651327cef9fb3d77e9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.